cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.NE 

This paper is about automatic dialogue evaluation, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper proposes a method for continual learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) that focuses on learning from a stream of data. The paper also involves training neural networks (cs.NE) and fine-tuning their parameters (cs.AI) for better performance. Finally, the paper discusses the resource efficiency of the proposed method, which could be relevant to the subfield of software engineering (cs.SD).
